Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖...滿了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩的願望改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是契約是不能改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想去的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直就像是詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要去我該去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...

