Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[明天到來的日子....]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽讓我們來把被褥收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被褥?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼空房間裡會有被褥...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生幫我們拿下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和君 手臂的傷已經好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 已經過了一個月了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想為那個空房間找個租戶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房間 在清和君來以前就一直空著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人住的話 房間會很快變舊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲小姐 我有空就會去為那房間通風的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以暫時先這樣空著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...說了些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和 好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你沒參加教授的研討會 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想做律師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你最近都沒有記筆記的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒怎麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像丟了魂一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 畢竟是失去了重要的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過去三個月了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊 保育園的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我沒太在意的 只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們說很想看現在保育園變成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君 我啊 想重建艾草保育園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖浦他...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這次會全力支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 籐本君也要振作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你最近在學校裡總是沒精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等準備得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起再去遠足一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 大家一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 大家一起遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 要去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿裡奈也要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去遠足啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太刁難人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 會加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都不記得那個傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 好像不是來送報紙的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不記得那傢伙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼只有你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想問的就是這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有更重要的事要問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像確實說過必須去一個該去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的想知道真相的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要為接下來所說的內容感到吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾經在人間界以外的地方遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去生命...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩的願望 那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越時空轉生到喜歡的人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小鳩的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 為了實現這個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受試煉 被允許來到此地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四季輪迴一次的時間內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有短暫的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙已經...去那裡了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和琇一郎先生在之前的長久歲月中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不知經歷過多少次悲傷的分別了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琇一郎...是那位醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每次琇一郎轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 每轉生一次 就再邂逅一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心在互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算已經失去了前世的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是仍舊是擁有相同靈魂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要隨著靈魂的指引前行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一定可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果工廠的機器再被這樣扣押下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼辦才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多虧了吹田律師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來也請您加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一會兒整理也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看一下桌上的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出個遠門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把那件案子托給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是關於遺產繼承的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 他是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 山內先生是第一次見到他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到我們事務所差不多要四年了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還很年輕但是已經很幹練了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是吹田律師事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓我家兒子跟人家學學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法院的服部書記官來的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些日子去世的委託人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於他兒子夫婦也去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然於二年前重新修改了遺囑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將所有的遺產留給孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是關於不動產的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為委託人的家族歷史久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地分界也有些曖昧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 我去當地看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春笑花　夏廣空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天綻放的鮮花　夏天寬廣的天空哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是律師事務所的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好...初次見面...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是前世的記憶已經失去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生是...我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴彈得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我擅自就彈起來了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首曲子 我總覺得好像曾經聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一個對我來說很重要的人唱給我聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在尋找那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 要是能找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 能讓我看一下房子內部嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就回事務所辦理剩下的手續了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個也...要還給你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 能再唱一次那首歌給我聽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:48.49,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}春に咲く花　夏広がる空よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:48.49,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}春天綻放的鮮花　夏天寬廣的天空哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:20:01.73,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}心の中に刻まれて煌めく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:20:01.73,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}在心中閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:15.23,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}朝に降る雨　窓を閉ざす日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:15.23,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}哪怕清晨下起雨　關起窗戶的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:28.91,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}胸にあふれる光は雲の上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:28.91,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}充滿胸中的光在雲層之上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最想陪伴的人所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總想著如果能再見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要笑著說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...果然好沒用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我等了這麼多年 遲到得好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生!

Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:22:00.86,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}喜び悲しみ　すべて抱いて歩いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:22:00.86,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}喜悦與悲傷　懷抱一切不停前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:14.62,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}私の手と君の手を　強く繋ぐもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:14.62,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}我和你的手 緊緊握在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:40.61,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}秋は水辺に　冬梢に潜む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.12,0:00:00.12,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}秋天在水邊 冬天寒枝上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:53.60,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}世界の奥の　限りない優しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:53.60,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}世界的深處 無限的博愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:23:06.87,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}夜がくるたび　祈りを捧げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:23:06.87,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}當夜幕降臨 我們來祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那個笨蛋完成了使命以後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想暗中守護那女孩 還要留在人間界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我們也要一直開著這蛋糕店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:20.47,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あしたくる日を　静かに迎えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:20.47,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}平和地迎接 嶄新的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦 年輪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子我 一百分滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:34.40,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}わたしを導く　遠い遠い呼び声よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:34.40,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}引導我的遙遠的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:47.63,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}微笑むように　歌うように　響く風の音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:47.63,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好像在微笑好像在歌唱一樣的風聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:24:00.47,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}喜び悲しみ　すべて抱いて歩いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:24:00.47,sss,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}喜悦與悲傷　懷抱一切不停前行
